76
00:05:39,140 --> 00:05:41,601
Now, so one of the first things that we recommend is a preamble.

77
00:05:41,661 --> 00:05:43,042
A preamble is not required.

78
00:05:43,462 --> 00:05:58,508
It doesn't necessarily have any sort of legal weight on the operation of the city, but it can be a good place for a community to share its collective vision for what it wants the city to be, what it wants to explain to the community how it wants to operate.

79
00:05:59,268 --> 00:06:01,949
