89
00:06:46,149 --> 00:06:49,735
So, the next section fairly self explanatory.

90
00:06:51,115 --> 00:07:08,873
really a section about the incorporation, the powers of the city, how the city's powers are divided, particularly between the executive and the legislative branch, and as well as what actually often tends to be very important is definitions for terms used throughout the charter.

91
00:07:09,994 --> 00:07:13,698
This is often an important, can be an important sticking point

92
00:07:15,579 --> 00:07:27,807
as cities sort of wrestle with some of these issues, particularly the executive's authority with regard to the city council, the legislative body.

93
00:07:30,408 --> 00:07:35,892
So going into Article 2, the legislative branch, again, the existing charter

94
00:07:36,880 --> 00:07:43,081
is very short with regard to the existence and the operation of the city council.

95
00:07:43,641 --> 00:07:47,322
