are of no longer of any effect because state law has been since changed, and it's state law that would govern.

195
00:19:46,446 --> 00:19:59,671
So that's, that's another reason to move forward with something that's referred to here as as modern, but, but does capture in one document, you know the fundamental features of the government.

196
00:20:02,432 --> 00:20:03,293
Great, thank you.

197
00:20:06,026 --> 00:20:18,010
